    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">"I did not say there was not a crisis." That is not good enough. He did not say there was; he did not tell them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-75f4a525-1a59-44dc-bd2a-afe20723237d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
