<p class="">What I said was—and here is a quotation from the "Manchester Guardian": "The Economic situation is serious." That is exactly contrary to what the right hon. Gentleman said that I said. I did say so. I pointed that out.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
