            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1c9e0b56-79b4-4294-9ca3-14da9ff7ad9a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
