        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3ee18dcf-d861-4f79-8097-697e3d9fa225">
                Mr. R. A. Butler
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3ee18dcf-d861-4f79-8097-697e3d9fa225" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-01-31/debates/8699fdfb-44fc-4f63-b97d-59e2bb57bf9b/FinancialAndEconomicSituation#contribution-3ee18dcf-d861-4f79-8097-697e3d9fa225">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">To which economy is the right hon. Gentleman referring? I understand that these economies have not been approved by the Minister of Education, and when he makes wild charges he should substantiate them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3ee18dcf-d861-4f79-8097-697e3d9fa225" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-01-31/debates/8699fdfb-44fc-4f63-b97d-59e2bb57bf9b/FinancialAndEconomicSituation#contribution-3ee18dcf-d861-4f79-8097-697e3d9fa225">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
